{{DISPLAYTITLE:List of ''Monk'' episodes}} The following is a complete '''episode list''' for the [[criminal]] [[Comedy-drama|dramedy]] [[television series]], '''''[[Monk (TV series)|Monk]]'''''. It premiered on [[USA Network]] July 12, 2002 in the [[United States]] and ended with a two-part series finale on November 27 and December 4, 2009. The complete series has a total of 125 episodes, including three 2-part episodes and four [[Christmas]] specials.
