==Webisodes== The first four of these webisodes were also released on the Season 5 DVD.
* Mr. Monk and Dr. Kroger * Mr. Monk and the Computer * Mr. Monk and the Blood Test * Mr. Monk Goes to the Gym * Mr. Monk and the Book Signing * Mr. Monk at the Party * Mr. Monk at the Diner
===''Little Monk''=== USA Network ordered ten webisodes that would deal with the Monk brothers' childhood. The first premiered on August 21, 2009. The series starred Aaron Linker as [[Adrian Monk|Little Monk]] and Chris Lizardi as [[Ambrose Monk|Little Ambrose]], and featured [[Bella Thorne]] as Wendy, one of the Monks' classmates. The series was directed by Randall Zisk, with Hy Conrad, Andy Breckman, Kevin Albright, and Justin Brenneman serving as writers. Aaron Linker had a chance of stardom on the actual show, where he appeared in a flashback once again as Little Monk. The webisodes are available only on the "Best of Monk" DVD. {| class="wikitable" style="width: 98%;" |-style="color:white" ! width="5%" style="background-color: #123456" | # ! style="background-color: #123456" | Title ! width="15%" style="background-color: #123456" | Writer ! width="15%" style="background-color: #123456" | Director ! width="25%" style="background-color: #123456" | Original airdate
